Guys I downloaded the game 2 days ago and I ended it today with no problems... However, I faced some difficulties with the installation but I have figured it out... To those who have Windows Vista and have problems with the crack:
1) Go to the following link: http://1337x.org/torrent/221943/Harry-Potter-and-The-Deathly-Hallows-Part-2-Proper-RELOADED-Crack-Only/ 

2) Download the Crack via torrent

3) Copy all the files which are inside the Crack folder (DONT COPY THE FILE)

4) Go to the place where the game is installed (My computer/C:/Program Files/Electronic Arts/Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows(TM) - Part 2

5) Now go to the file named ''pc''

6) Paste the files that you have copied
Note: These files have to overwrite the similar ones which are already inside the folder. So if a note pop up while copying asking you to overwrite click ''overwrite''. This will happen only if some of the files you copied already exist in the ''pc'' file.

7) Run the file ''hp8''

8) Play the game

If someone has any other problems with installment in Vista send me a message.. :) :)
